Get 45% off the Magic Mind bundle with with my link: [https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN](https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN)   
  
As 2025 kicks off, the Major Issues Podcast crew dons their fortune-telling hats to predict which comic book movies, TV shows, and series will hit the mark—or miss it entirely! From long-awaited sequels to ambitious new adaptations, the hosts break down the upcoming slate of projects and assess their chances of success. Will the box office crown a new champion? Which streaming show will dominate fandom conversations? And what could surprise everyone by flopping? Tune in for hot takes, bold predictions, and a glimpse into the future of comic book media!  
  
2024 is in the BOOKS, but that means we have a brand new year ahead of us and with it a brand new slew of amazing comic book content! Join us as we do our best to predict the hits and misses of 2025 before they happen in this extra special episode of the Major Issues Podcast!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

